item.description:
After 7 years of service, my employer grants me a one month paid sabbatical that I can back with a month of vacation time. That&rsquo;s two months paid time off! I&rsquo;m taking my sabbatical time in September and October. I keep getting asked, &ldquo;What are you planning to do?&rdquo;
The answer, of course, is coffee-related.
Two months is a long time, but also a short time. I plan to learn as much about the coffee industry as possible, tracing backwards from cup to farm.
